
Please read the documentation in doc/ & docs/

Building userland: 

	make programs install

Building KLIPS kernel module on 2.4 (assuming your kernel source is /usr/src/linux-2.4)

	make KERNELSRC=/usr/src/linux-2.4 module minstall

Building KLIPS kernel module on 2.6

	make KERNELSRC=/lib/modules/`uname -r`/build module minstall


Build requirements:
gmp-devel bison flex redhat-rpm-config pkgconfig gcc make xmlto

for systemd: pkgconfig hostname systemd
for nss: nss-devel >= 3.12.6-2, nspr-devel
for pam/xauth: pam-devel
for dnssec: unbound-devel
for FIPS support: fipscheck-devel
for libcap-ng support: libcap-ng-devel
for CRL fetching support: openldap-devel curl-devel

Testing runtime requirements:

kvm, qemu, libvirt, virt-manager, sudo, pexpect, python-setproctitle, sudo, bridge-utils
